{"tid":2393830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"照顧者其實都好需要俾人體諒","createTime":"2021-02-03T18:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T23:29:22.000Z","uid":201309,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"512ba6af192c7bb9ef97afa7b10b558254e2cae8","tid":2393830,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"借人ac代post<br />\n<br />\n屋企長輩同我哋一齊住咗都好耐吓<br />\n隨住日子耐咗 佢身體出現問題<br />\n脾氣差不特止 排泄物可以整到四圍都係<br />\n<br />\n老人家做被照顧者 <br />\n個心係會唔安樂 會覺得自己冇用<br />\n但起碼叫做有人照顧<br />\n<br />\n但照顧佢嘅人嘅感受往往俾人忽視<br />\n得到嘅係更多來自被照顧者嘅不滿同謾罵<br />\n<br />\n思考緊應唔應該直接同佢講送佢去老人院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdc6f185725a46135f106e814e2d2f1b3edbb4a","tid":2393830,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"有冇人面對緊一樣嘅處境<br />\n入嚟分享吓"},{"pid":"43cb783a25ed6c59eaff8e309825a73557adfcc0","tid":2393830,"uid":201309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"如果佢個格唔好咁閪都可以諗吓請外面嘅人嚟照顧<br />\n<br />\n但佢性格真係太閪太仆街<br />\n唔知可以喺邊度請人幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1aa1a28f1c50ed333dfb6747aa569f408ac18c","tid":2393830,"uid":201309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:36:37.000Z","msg":"頭都大鳩埋<br />\n好撚辛苦<br />\n本身一家人都開開心心<br />\n而家佢一個人成日抱怨 成日屌鳩人<br />\n搞到我 我老豆老母 我細佬都唔開心"},{"pid":"7ffc1ed8343def95af8dcccfe21d6b4626541e48","tid":2393830,"uid":36324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:37:55.000Z","msg":"巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737787fbfaa63b45242bfdada82d8655622cde0a","tid":2393830,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ffc1ed8343def95af8dcccfe21d6b4626541e48","tid":2393830,"uid":36324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:37:55.000Z","msg":"巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj